that if we already set the output sink to 'user in gdb-stopping, that is fine."
  (setq gud-running nil)
  (let ((sink gdb-output-sink))
    (cond
     ((eq sink 'inferior)
      (setq gdb-output-sink 'user))
     ((eq sink 'user) t)
